```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    Note right of browser: The browser sends the new note as JSON data via an asynchronous XHR/fetch request
    server-->>browser: 201 Created, the new note as JSON
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: The browser executes the callback function that adds the new note to the notes list, without reloading the page
```
